      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i just feel like i've been doing everything right lately with my diet and stuff so my blood must be fine. i dont want to keep taking such a high dose if it's actually more than i need. like, if i just slowly taper down to 2mg, wouldn't that be a safer way to test if i still need it? it seems pretty logical to just scale back when everything is stable.",
